title: Lemon-Herb Protein Roast — Low-Carb Edition 1
hydrationTip: Pair with 300–500 ml water to support low-carb digestion.
method: Preheat oven to 200°C.
Toss vegetables with olive oil, herbs, salt, and pepper.
Add chicken on top of the vegetables.
Roast until chicken is cooked through.
Slice and portion into four meal containers.
swaps: Replace chicken with turkey or tofu.
Swap broccoli for spinach.
Add chilli flakes for additional heat.
